# Atomic Dustbin Dan

HTML5 Game inspired by Atari's "Gauntlet" arcade game, with my own dream enhancements.

## Files
- `atomic-dustbin-dan.html` - Main game file
- `atomic-dustbin-dan-STATUS.md` - Project status and progress
- `Atomic-Dustbin-Dan-GDD.md` - Game design document

## Running
Open `atomic-dustbin-dan.html` in a browser.

